track_notes: Easy familly walk, no much ascent, few rocks and a nice point of view
track_title: Mont Castello near Berre les Alpes

track_notes: This is a very short walk to the summit, may be you have to look for the trig point that is not so easy to found. If the ground is wet, be carefull because it is very slippy. about jannuary or february you will walk in mimosas trees! There is one one or two places for cars to park and there is some nice and fresh water very close!
Plenty room at the village to park, and a nice walk the long of the small road. Nice houses and garden!
